- @sub_title = "#{@inv_user.name} 邀请你上岛测试，发现真实的自己"
- content_for :site_layout, "start_page registation_dom"

- css "user"

- content_for :content, do
  .registation_intro{:style => "background:url(/images/registation1.jpg) no-repeat"}
    .registation_logo
    
  .registation_title
    %span.txt
      = "#{@inv_user.name} 邀请你上岛测试，发现真实的自己"
   
  = form_for(@user, :url => users_path, :html => {:class => 'registation'}) do |f|
    .item
      .nick_box
        = f.label :name, '用户名'
        = f.text_field :name
      .error
        &nbsp;
        = @user.errors[:name].first
    .item
      .email_box
        = f.label :email, '邮箱'
        = f.text_field :email
      .error
        &nbsp;
        = @user.errors[:email].first
    .item
      .password_box
        = f.label :password, '密码'
        = f.password_field :password
      .error
        &nbsp;
        = @user.errors[:password].first
    = hidden_field_tag 'code', @inv_user.inv_code
    = hidden_field_tag 'refer', request.referer
    .submit_box
      = f.submit "注册"
  .registation_txt
    在宽岛上，你可以简单地发布清晰的图片，建立多个页面来展示你的个性和爱好，同和你有共同兴趣的人们认识并交流⋯⋯
